["setState is called directly inside \"useEffect\". Synchronous setState in effects causes an extra re-render. Consider deriving the value during render or moving the update into a callback.", "Values derived from props and state should be calculated during render, not in an effect. (https://react.dev/learn/you-might-not-need-an-effect)"]
